> Module Eligibility

> Using Earnings

# Synthetic two-module eligibility

## Declarations

```catala-metadata
declaration scope DetermineEligibility:
  input gross_earned_income content money
  input household_size content integer
  internal earnings_result content Earnings.EarningsResult
  internal income_limit content money
  internal income_eligible condition
  output is_eligible condition
```

## Sub-module call

*Source: policy.md — Section 1. Earnings exclusions*

```catala
scope DetermineEligibility:
  definition earnings_result equals
    (output of Earnings.ApplyExclusions
      with { -- gross_earned_income: gross_earned_income }).result
```

## Income threshold

*Source: policy.md — Section 2. Income threshold*

```catala
scope DetermineEligibility:
  definition income_limit equals
    $943 + (decimal of (household_size - 1)) * $360

  rule income_eligible
    under condition earnings_result.remaining_earned_income < income_limit
    consequence fulfilled
```

## Decision

*Source: policy.md — Section 3. Decision*

```catala
scope DetermineEligibility:
  rule is_eligible
    under condition income_eligible
    consequence fulfilled
```
